01:38:58.876 --> 01:39:01.238
[SPEAKER_14]: programme of a country in the Middle East.

01:39:01.638 --> 01:39:06.302
[SPEAKER_14]: The multilateral institution is needed at that time.

01:39:06.742 --> 01:39:10.445
[SPEAKER_14]: So, a moment of choice and let's make the right decision.

01:39:11.184 --> 01:39:12.324
[SPEAKER_10]: And the time is up.

01:39:12.484 --> 01:39:13.044
[SPEAKER_10]: Wow.

01:39:13.124 --> 01:39:18.385
[SPEAKER_10]: We have heard from the five candidates who are here with us here in Jeju.

01:39:18.485 --> 01:39:21.626
[SPEAKER_10]: It was always going to be a struggle to keep you all on time.

01:39:21.946 --> 01:39:34.709
[SPEAKER_10]: I have to say we're only 10 minutes over, but thank you all and best of luck to all six of the candidates who are vying for this very crucial role as the next Secretary General of the United Nations.

01:39:34.949 --> 01:39:40.630
[SPEAKER_10]: As we heard from Ban Ki-moon himself, he doesn't envy you, but I'm sure you'll all do as

01:39:41.733 --> 01:39:41.974
[SPEAKER_10]: job.

01:39:42.396 --> 01:39:44.806
[SPEAKER_10]: Once again, a big round of applause to our candidates, please.

